description: The BEST Baja style fish tacos this side of the border! Original, flavorful, amazing. Great award winning salsa.CASANOVA Fish Tacos objective is to bring to the customer the real Baja style fish taco experience. The blend of spices used in the batter has been a 3 year process to become perfected. The famous and most flavorful spicy pico de gallo which is customer favorite, the tomatillo based salsa with habanero for that extra kick and 3rd place winner at the 2010 Del Mair Fair and the secret white sauce are all  original recipes created from scratch.  CASANOVA Fish Tacos will be the last fish taco you will ever want to have.  In order to provide the best quality of the product, we cook and deep fry on site.  That way you always get it fresh. Our service includes but is not limited to: Plates, nakpins, forks, chips, two types of salsas, lime wedges, secret white sauce, and a 1 or 2  hour all you can eat feast.  The only item you provide is the beverage for your event.
name: Casanova Fish Tacos
